HOME_P_1: TickTwo is Europe's favourite airline and train service, operating more than 1,800 daily flights from 76 bases, connecting 200 destinations in 31 countries on a fleet of over 300 Boeing 737 aircraft. TickTwo has orders for a further 380 new Boeing 737 aircraft, which will enable TickTwo to lower fares and grow traffic from 105m this year to 180m p.a. in FY24. TickTwo has a team of more than 10,000 highly skilled aviation professionals delivering Europe's No.1 on-time performance, and has an industry leading 30-year safety record.
HOME_P_2: Kings and presidents have indulged on this magnificent, moving five-star "hotel-on-wheels" and "hotel-in-sky". From love-struck honeymooners, to adulated celebrities. And even ordinary folk who romanticise about a life of spectacular luxury, a life that has seemed tantalisingly out of reach. Until now...
HOME_P_3: Welcome aboard TickTwo. Your unforgettable experience is about to begin...
ABOUT_P_1: TickTwo. You know who we are. You know what we do. You know that when you travel with TickTwo you'll get where you want to go cheaply, reliably and without any fuss.
ABOUT_P_2: Our no frills, low cost model revolutionized the air travel industry and opened up Europe to the masses. And we continue to lead the way in great value travel, doing whatever it takes to guarantee that our fares are the lowest out there.
ABOUT_P_3: But our fares aren't the only thing that sets us apart. We can also boast the most on-time flights of any airline in Europe, an industry leading 30-year safety record, first class punctuality, near perfect baggage handling and an innovative, cutting edge green policy.
